This folder includes the makefile for the publisher and subscriber for the kinect.  simply type make all to build it, and make run to, well, I think you get the idea...

1) Run ./setup_kinect_dependencies_all.sh in the setup folder

2) Run ./setup_environment_kinect.sh in the setup folder

3) cd over to the libs folder and enter the libfreenect folder

4) Run ./fullBuild.sh

5) cd over to the /drivers/kinect/ folder and type make

6) type 'make run' or simply find the exectuables in the bin folder
